{"tid":2490752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（更新）一家六口四人不治 男戶主接獲通知回家營救家人不果 吸入濃煙情況危殆","createTime":"2021-04-16T00:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T01:05:27.000Z","uid":391580,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2533d4ccacfac51d79e077de3c99cf24b8844b6b","tid":2490752,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T00:08:47.000Z","msg":"現場為寶達邨達喜樓5樓一單位，據悉住有一家六口，包括男戶主、其妻子、女兒、姨仔、外父及外母。凌晨約3時04分，該單位突然起火，火勢十分猛烈，傳出大量濃煙，大批居民報警表示被困。消防員接報趕抵，動用一隊煙帽隊及一條喉灌救，及至凌晨約3時59分將火救熄。<br />\n<br />\n起火單位6人傷亡慘重，警方證實，1名女子在現場被證實死亡、3名女子被送往聯合醫院搶救後，均告不治，當中包括1名女童。就現場所見，1名嚴重燒傷的人士，送院時已手部僵硬，毫無反應。據了解，起火單位老翁及時逃生，他感不適，清醒被送往聯合醫院治理。<span class=\"red\"><strong>而中年男戶主當時並不在家，接獲家人求救後，立即趕回家中，但全屋已陷火海，他營救無果，全臉更被熏黑，情緒十分激動，送往將軍澳醫院搶救後，情況危殆</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeWfLz2NYo3x1jzPheiqkbLEp8hyHGt9yjmkX7FjVKqBE?filename=zFaX75S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzFaX75S.jpg&h=3424678f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14116fb422a13e9dde54f9d36dc6b4e979a8e5de","tid":2490752,"uid":10905,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T00:10:46.000Z","msg":"都幾撚肯定係新香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0e6098b5a9649b003c192b67515c2bdc51709e","tid":2490752,"uid":188310,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T00:11:42.000Z","msg":"戚家冚家剷阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff116ef0bb24e7e71e0556db6c6e3f7d19c40270","tid":2490752,"uid":284607,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T00:12:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass